<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdikeit
                        brief, den ir und <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>vette<ex>r,</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedig <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog
                        Ernst und <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan> Wilhelm, <add>uns</add> gesant
                        habt von der <expan>czweyu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wegen, als czwischen ew und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Osterreich, ist,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und senden
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<add><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></add> Hansen
                                <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        diener, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> davon czu reden. Und
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc., waz der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sach czu <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> mal an ew werb von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Ernst<ex>en</ex></expan> und herczog Wilhelm,
